    {
      "id": "redirect-flow-details",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 550,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "1. Redis GET url:{code}  → cache HIT (< 1ms)\n2. Redis INCR clicks:{code}  (fire & forget)\n3. Return 301 redirect\n\nTotal: ~2ms  |  Zero Postgres queries\nCache MISS: fallback to Replica read → ~10ms",
