      "text": "Redirect (cache hit): ~2ms   |   Redirect (cache miss): ~10ms   |   Create: ~15ms\nIDs/sec/worker: 4,096,000    |   Workers: up to 1,024           |   Redis: 100K+ ops/sec/node\nStorage: 500B/URL → 1B URLs = 500GB   |   Cache: hot 20% → 100GB RAM at 1B scale",
